  <summary>XFCE Dock icon manager</summary>
  <summary xml:lang="es">Gestor de iconos para el dock de XFCE</summary>
  <summary xml:lang="fr">Gestionnaire d'icônes pour le plugin Docklike XFCE</summary>
  <summary xml:lang="pt">Gerenciador de ícones para o plugin Docklike do XFCE</summary>
  <summary xml:lang="de">Icon-Manager für das XFCE Docklike Plugin</summary>
